LocalizedStateSelect
=============
 localized_state_select gem allows you to easily create dropdown list of states for a country provided as an option.
 Default counrty is US.

 Usage:
 localized_state_select(object, method, country='US', options = {}, html_options = {})
  
	Currently it supports only US, CANADA

 If you want to add other country plese send me the list of states and I will add them, or you can fork and make a pull request.

